snippet.title: Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde by Robert Louis Stevenson ~book review
snippet.description:
Utterson thinks it's strange that his best friend, Dr Jekyll, would leave his entire fortune to a Mr. Hyde, someone Utterson has never heard of.  Tales of violence and misdeeds seem to surround Hyde.  Utterson investigates the mysterious stranger, but what he finds may more gruesome than he could fathom.    

Audiobook narrated by Ian Holm.
